quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Itegeko rya Allah (ryo kuza kw’imperuka) riregereje, bityo ntimuryihutishe. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe kandi ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya nabyo"
  16,2,"Ku bw’itegeko rye, (Allah) amanura malayika (Gaburiheli) azanye ubutumwa k’uwo (Allah) ashaka mu bagaragu be (agira ati) \"Muburire (abantu) ko nta yindi mana (ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri) usibye njye; bityo nimuntinye"
  16,3,Yaremye ibirere n’isi ku mpamvu z’ukuri. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe kandi ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya nabyo
  16,4,"Yeremye umuntu amukomoye mu ntanga, none uwo (muntu) yahisemo kuba umunyempaka ugaragara (mu guhakana izuka)"
  16,5,"(Allah) yanabaremeye amatungo; muri yo harimo ibibatera gususuruka (imyambaro) n’ibindi bibafitiye akamaro, ndetse hari n’ayo murya"
  16,6,Munashimishwa n’ubwiza bwayo igihe muyacyuye nimugoroba n’igihe muyahuye mu gitondo
  16,7,"Anikorera imitwaro yanyu iremereye akayijyana aho mutari gushobora kugera bitabagoye. Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wanyu ni Nyir’impuhwe zihebuje,Nyir’imbabazi"
  16,8,"(Yanaremye) ifarasi, icyimanyi (cy’ifarasi n’indogobe) ndetse n’indogobe; kugira ngo mubigendereho, kandi binababere imitako. Yanaremyen’ibindi bintu mutazi"
  16,9,"Allah ni we werekana inzira igororotse, ariko hari n’izindi zigoramye. Kandi iyo aza kubishaka yari kubayobora mwese"
  16,10,"Ni we umanura amazi (imvura) aturutse mu kirere, mukayanywa ndetse akanameza ibimera muragiramo amatungo yanyu"
  16,11,"Ayameresha ibihingwa, imizeti, imitende, imizabibu ndetse na buri bwoko bw’imbuto. Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bantu batekereza"
  16,12,"Kandi yaborohereje ijoro (kugira ngo mubashe kuruhuka) n’amanywa (kugira ngo mubashe gukora), izuba n’ukwezi (kugira ngo bibamurikire), ndetse n’inyenyeri zorohejwe ku bw’itegeko rye. Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bantu bafite ubwenge"
  16,13,"Kandi ibyo yabaremeye ku isi (haba mu matungo, ibihingwa n’amabuye y’agaciro) bifite amabara atandukanye. Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bantu bazirikana (ubumwe bw’Imana no kuba ari yo yonyine ikwiye gusengwa)"
  16,14,"Ni na we woroheje inyanja kugira ngo (mukuremo) inyama z’umwimerere (amafi) muzirye, munakuremo imitako mwambara. Kandi ubona amato azihinguranya kugira ngo mushakishe ingabire ze,no kugira ngo mubashe gushimira"
  16,15,"Yanashyize imisozi ku isi irayishimangira kugira ngo itabahungabanya, (anayishyiramo) imigezi (kugira ngo munywe amazi yayo), ndetse n’inzira kugira ngo zibayobore (aho mugana)"
  16,16,(Yanabashyiriyeho) ibimenyetso (bibayobora ku manywa) ndetse n’inyenyeri (zibayobora nijoro) kugira ngo bayoboke (aho bagana)
  16,17,Nonese ubwo (Allah) urema wamugereranya (n’ibigirwamana) bitarema? Ese ntimutekereza
  16,18,"Kandi muramutse mushatse kubarura ingabire za Allah(yabahaye) ntimwazihetura. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  16,19,Kandi Allah azi ibyo muhisha n’ibyo mugaragaza
  16,20,"Na babandi basenga ibitari Allah, ntacyo byigeze biremaahubwo na byo byararemwe"
  16,21,"Ni ibipfu, nta buzima bifite kandi ntibinazi igihe (ababisengaga) bazazurirwa"
  16,22,"Imana yanyu ni Imana imwe. Ariko babandi batemera imperuka, imitima ya bo ihakana (ubumwe bwa Allah), kandi basabitswe n’ubwibone"
  16,23,"Nta gushidikanya ko Allah azi ibyo bahisha n’ibyo bagaragaza. Mu by’ukuri, ntakunda abibone"
  16,24,"N’iyo babwiwe bati \"Niiki Nyagasani wanyu yahishuriye (Muhamadi)? \"Baravuga bati \"Ni imigani y’abo hambere"
  16,25,Ku munsi w’imperuka bazikorera imitwaro (ibyaha) yabo uko yakabaye ndetse n’imitwaro y’abo bayobeje kubera kutagira ubumenyi. Mbega ububi bw’ibyo bazaba bikoreye
  16,26,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi babayeho mbere yabo bacuriye imigambi mibisha (intumwa zabo), nuko Allah arimbura inyubako zabo ahereye mu misingi, maze ibisenge bibagwa hejuru, nuko ibihano bibageraho biturutse aho batakekaga"
  16,27,"Hanyuma, ku munsi w’imperuka (Allah) azabasuzuguza maze ababwire ati \"Ibigirwamana mwajyaga mumbangikanya na byo, murwanya (intumwa n’abemera) kubera byo, biri he? Babandi bahawe ubumenyi (bujyanye n’ukwemera) bazavuga bati \"Ugusuzugurika n’ingorane kuri uyu munsi biri ku bahakanyi"
  16,28,"Babandi abamalayika bakuramo roho barihemukiye (bakora ibyaha)\". Bazicisha bugufi (bagira bati) \"Nta kibi twajyaga dukora!\" (Abamalayika bazasubiza bati) \"Oya! (Murabeshya) mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibyo mwakoraga"
  16,29,"Ngaho nimwinjire mu miryango y’umuriro wa Jahanama, muzabamo ubuziraherezo, kandi ni cyo cyicaro kibi cy’abibone"